Serializable
public class DefaultFormatter
extends Function

A simple javascript function intended to use as tooltip formatter. If used as tooltip formatter, the series name and the currently selected y value are displayed as tooltip.

Example: "Series: 4".

Author:
Tom Hombergs (tom.hombergs@gmail.com)
